'''天主教加爾維斯頓-休斯敦總教區'''（{{lang-la|Archidioecesis Galvestoniensis Houstoniensis}}；{{lang-en|Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Galveston-Houston}}）是[[美國|美國]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]]教省[[總教區|總教區]]，也是該國三十二個總教區之一。

總教區於2017年時管轄[[德克薩斯州|德克薩斯州]]共十個縣<ref name="ArchFacts">{{cite web |title=Facts and Figures |url=https://www.archgh.org/about/about-us/facts-and-figures/ |publisher=The Archdiocese of Galveston-Houston |accessdate=2020-01-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200130145616/https://www.archgh.org/about/about-us/facts-and-figures/ |archivedate=2020-01-30 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並轄六個教區。總教區的面積為8,880平方英里，2017年時有177萬9284名教友（佔總教區人口）、146個堂區和435名司鐸。<ref name="ArchFacts" />現任總主教為[[達尼爾·尼各老·迪納爾多|達尼爾·尼各老·迪納爾多]][[樞機|樞機]]<ref name="Miranda20071124">{{cite web |last1=Miranda |first1=Salvador |title=Consistory of November 24, 2007 (II) |url=https://webdept.fiu.edu/~mirandas/bios2007.htm |publisher=Florida International University |accessdate=2020-01-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200130104521/https://webdept.fiu.edu/~mirandas/bios2007.htm |archivedate=2020-01-30 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>，輔理主教為{{link-en|喬治·謝爾特斯|George Sheltz|喬治·A·謝爾特斯}}<ref>{{cite web |title=Auxiliary Bishop George A. Sheltz |url=https://www.archgh.org/about/our-bishops/auxiliary-bishop-sheltz/ |publisher=The Archdiocese of Galveston-Houston |accessdate=2020-01-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200130110534/https://www.archgh.org/about/our-bishops/auxiliary-bishop-sheltz/ |archivedate=2020-01-30 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休總主教為{{link-en|若瑟·菲奧倫薩|Joseph Fiorenza|若瑟·A·菲奧倫薩}}<ref>{{cite web |title=Archbishop Emeritus Joseph A. Fiorenza |url=https://www.archgh.org/about/our-bishops/archbishop-emeritus-fiorenza/ |publisher=The Archdiocese of Galveston-Houston |accessdate=2020-01-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200130113059/https://www.archgh.org/about/our-bishops/archbishop-emeritus-fiorenza/ |archivedate=2020-01-30 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休輔理主教為{{link-en|雲先·M·里佐托|Vincent M. Rizzotto}}<ref>{{cite web |title=Retired Auxiliary Bishop of Galveston-Houston |url=https://www.archgh.org/about/our-bishops/retired-bishop-rizzotto/ |publisher=The Archdiocese of Galveston-Houston |accessdate=2020-01-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200130121722/https://www.archgh.org/about/our-bishops/retired-bishop-rizzotto/ |archivedate=2020-01-30 |language=en |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

'''德克薩斯宗座監牧區'''於1839年設立，1842年升為宗座代牧區。代牧區於1847年升為教區，稱為'''加爾維斯頓教區'''。教區於1959年易名為加爾維斯頓-休斯敦教區，2004年12月29日升為總教區。<ref>{{cite web |title=History |url=https://www.archgh.org/about/about-us/history/ |publisher=The Archdiocese of Galveston-Houston |accessdate=2020-01-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200130124804/https://www.archgh.org/about/about-us/history/ |archivedate=2020-01-30 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>

